 Detailed sources: Data submitted by FSC and PEFC secretariats (certifying bodies) to FAO, Global Forest Resources Assessment No data on certified forest area in the FSC and PEFC records, value is therefore assumed to be zero Data submitted by the Forestry Agency of Japan to FAO, Global Forest Resources Assessment Data from 2019 submitted by the Forestry Agency of Japan to FAO, Global Forest Resources Assessment
